              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "The `Moped::BSON::ObjecId.legal?` method in `mongodb/bson-ruby` before 3.0.4 as used in rubygem-moped allows remote attackers to cause a denial of service (worker resource consumption) via a crafted string. NOTE: This issue is due to an incomplete fix to CVE-2015-4410."
              },
