              "help": {
                "markdown": "The software loads data over a plain-text HTTP connection, without authenticity or integrity protection. An attacker may be able to hijack the connection.\n\n\n## Countermeasures\n\nUse an `https://` URL for all requests.\n\n## Additional information\n\n**[CWE-419](https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/419.html)**",
